@remark *** MACROS MENU HELP ***

@node MAIN "Menus:  Macros"

@{FG Highlight}Macros:@{FG Text}
@{code}
@{" Start Learning         " link STAR}  Begin recording a BME macro.
@{" Stop Learning...       " link STOP}  Stop recording a BME macro.

@{" BME Macros...          " link BMMA}  Install and execute BME macros.

@{" Execute ARexx Macro... " link EXAR}  Execute an ARexx script.

